1
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:32,360
It really is his.

2
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:34,430
Impossible.

3
00:00:35,130 --> 00:00:37,030
Eastern Wasteland is billions of miles away

4
00:00:37,030 --> 00:00:38,700
from Central Continent's Human Emperor City.

5
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:40,600
How could you arrive

6
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:42,600
with an army in such a short time?

7
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:43,960
Hmph.

8
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:46,030
Are billions of miles

9
00:00:46,530 --> 00:00:47,500
that far?

10
00:00:48,300 --> 00:00:49,830
My foundation is complete.

11
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:53,060
I can break into the Great Emperor Realm at any time.

12
00:00:53,230 --> 00:00:55,360
A spatial distance of billions of miles

13
00:00:55,360 --> 00:00:56,960
is but a fleeting moment.

14
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,100
He can actually break

15
00:00:58,100 --> 00:00:59,960
into the Great Emperor Realm at any time.

16
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:01,300
How on earth did he do it

17
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,930
in this current Age of Spiritual Depletion?

18
00:01:02,930 --> 00:01:05,830
I've honed myself in the Emperor Pass for thousands of years.

19
00:01:05,830 --> 00:01:08,330
I can barely stabilize at the early Quasi-Emperor stage,

20
00:01:08,330 --> 00:01:10,730
and reaching the middle stage is nowhere in sight.

21
00:01:10,730 --> 00:01:12,500
Yet he is already about to become an Emperor.

22
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:13,230
Gu Linyuan,

23
00:01:14,100 --> 00:01:15,700
how dare you!

24
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:20,760
I haven't even gone to the Eastern Wasteland to trouble you,

25
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:23,560
yet you dare lead an army to the Central Continent.

26
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:27,360
Do you really think this fully-armed Human Ancestral Court

27
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:29,620
is like your barbaric Eastern Wasteland

28
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:31,590
where you can do whatever you want?

29
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:32,729
Gu Linyuan,

30
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:34,560
you forced me to do this.

31
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:37,900
In the name of the Human Emperor,

32
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:39,360
I ignite the ancient pact!

33
00:01:39,900 --> 00:01:40,900
I decree all clans

34
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,600
to fight against the rebels!

35
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,200
Take this,

36
00:02:14,830 --> 00:02:16,430
and avenge your clan.

37
00:02:21,730 --> 00:02:22,630
Jiang Yun,

38
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,360
give me your life!

39
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,260
Kill!

40
00:02:43,829 --> 00:02:46,430
This isn't ordinary Quasi-Emperor pressure.

41
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,860
It's a resonance with the Heavenly Dao.

42
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:48,460
Could it be

43
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,660
that he wants to forcefully gather the Human Ancestral Court's

44
00:02:50,660 --> 00:02:53,530
residual luck accumulated over tens of thousands of years

45
00:02:53,530 --> 00:02:55,430
and undergo ultimate sublimation?

46
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,860
He wants to forcefully prove his Dao

47
00:02:56,860 --> 00:02:58,800
and become an Emperor in this era.

48
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,960
If Gu Linyuan becomes an Emperor,

49
00:03:07,130 --> 00:03:09,260
we will all die without a burial place.

50
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:12,030
We must not let him take that final step.

51
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,630
Sacrifice the origin

52
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:15,490
and activate the Emperor Weapon!

53
00:04:08,130 --> 00:04:11,130
The ancestors of the four great families have fallen.

54
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,500
The enemy is terrified.

55
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:13,600
Sons of the Gu family,

56
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,660
follow me and kill!

57
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:18,720
Gu Linyuan.

58
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:21,660
You led your army to shatter the Human Emperor City

59
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:23,200
and besiege the Ancestral Court.

60
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,730
Are you really going to rebel?

61
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:27,200
I am the destined Human Emperor, mandated by heaven.

62
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,260
If you dare touch a single hair on my head today,

63
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:30,730
it would be defying the Heavenly Dao.

64
00:04:30,730 --> 00:04:32,600
The spit of every cultivator in the world

65
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,530
could drown you.

66
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:36,960
For the sake of your Imperial Clan's past contributions,

67
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,560
I can let bygones be bygones.

68
00:04:44,130 --> 00:04:45,060
Ridiculous.

69
00:04:45,730 --> 00:04:47,159
Defying the Heavenly Dao?

70
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,600
The Heavenly Dao speaks not.

71
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,159
Today,

72
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,300
I will make it speak.
